gobblin.util

Class WritableShimSerialization

  • java.lang.Object
    • gobblin.util.WritableShimSerialization
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serialization<WritableShim>

    public class WritableShimSerialization
extends Object
implements Serialization<WritableShim>
    A serializer that understands how to write objects that implement WritableShim out to a Hadoop stream. This class must be present in the io.serializations key of a Hadoop config for the Hadoop runtime to find and instantiate it.
